OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with rain
OL,6,Fspreading east for a time. Drier this
OL,7,Fafternoon with some bright spells and
OL,8,Fa few showers, occasionally heavy. A
OL,9,Fcolder day.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome showery rain spreading
OL,12,Feast this evening, mainly across the
OL,13,Fwest with some high ground snow.
OL,14,FBecoming dry with clear periods during
OL,15,Fthe early hours. Cold with some frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FMainly dry with some sunshine
OL,18,Fin the morning. Dry but cloudier in
OL,19,Fthe afternoon. Strengthening winds
OL,20,Fextending northeast in the evening.
OL,21,FRather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
