OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain clearing on Saturday
OL,7,Fthen largely dry with sunny intervals.
OL,8,FBright spells and scattered showers on
OL,9,FSunday and Monday, but some dry
OL,10,Fweather too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
